{"title":"话短心长（诗两首）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":7,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"话短心长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（诗两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李欣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、送“敖特根”（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加全国群英会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送走了孩子的背影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也带去了妈妈的心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妈也想看看毛主席呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不只是疼念敖特根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）敖特根，蒙语：最小的儿子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、一个城市人民公社女社员的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是爱情有什么变化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个女人站起来啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还是一个女社员；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不只是你的她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的妈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老皇历看不得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女人并不比男人差。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}